ssets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 證明支拿已經冇得救"},{"pid":"cb3360afbba3b49c5f99b524adeabb65d0f31927","tid":791180,"uid":53705,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:05:10.000Z","msg":"日本入侵中國, 屠殺無數中國人<br />\n<br />\n毛澤東 都可以感謝日本侵華<br />\n<br />\n咁家陣習總 感謝美國打鳩中共, 都合情合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f3491f3810096db37af52f1682f100675d2b095","tid":791180,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:09:47.000Z","msg":"中國命令香港鎮政府也要跟隨黨的指示共同面對美國制裁。"},{"pid":"e9c6488e4f5804f7ca88a596ec1fad2eeae23e3c","tid":791180,"uid":75326,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"cb3360afbba3b49c5f99b524adeabb65d0f31927","tid":791180,"uid":53705,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:05:10.000Z","msg":"日本入侵中國, 屠殺無數中國人<br />\n<br />\n毛澤東 都可以感謝日本侵華<br />\n<br />\n咁家陣習總 感謝美國打鳩中共, 都合情合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T15:34:55.000Z","msg":"呢個「感謝川普」的而且確係事實<br />\n近百年黎中國所謂嘅不惜一切&quot;代價&quot;<br />\n響統治者口中&quot;代價&quot;都係指老百姓嘅生活<br />\n無論十四億食薯仔都好<br />\n中南海就永遠好似肥仔金一樣唔會少條毛<br />\n<br />\n但反而當&quot;倉稟實而知禮節，衣食足而知榮辱&quot;時間一到<br />\n因為人民覺醒而有更多需求時<br />\n最有危機又係中南海嘅統治者<br />\n所以經過卅年經濟發展之後<br />\n中國又係時候退翻去食薯仔階段<br />\n咁樣官媒又點可以唔要「感謝川普」?"},{"pid":"15bf02dc7cc3b7d6a77f0057a5f4e5ad234fde0b","tid":791180,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T22:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87448007689d8a5071522050f39d6a160de6ce8c","tid":791180,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T23:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e580fdc072ecfad1159436c4c8c08502476ad0b9","tid":791180,"uid":39777,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":